Opening Hours

  • Monday: Closed
  • Tuesday - Friday: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM
  • Saturday - Sunday: 9:00 AM - 7:00 PM
  • Public Holidays: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM

Last admission is 45 minutes before closing time.

Admission

General Admission

  • Adults: $15
  • Seniors (65+): $10
  • Students (with ID): $10
  • Children (under 12): Free

Special Exhibitions

Prices vary by exhibition. See individual exhibition pages for details.

Membership

Members enjoy free unlimited admission. Learn more about membership.

Tickets can be purchased online or at the museum entrance.

Location & Directions

123 Museum Street
City, State 12345
Phone: (123) 456-7890
Email: info@museum.com

Getting Here

Public Transportation

  • Subway: Lines A, B, C (Museum Station)
  • Bus: Routes 10, 20, 30 (Museum Stop)

By Car

Limited street parking is available. Public parking garages are located within a 5-minute walk.

Interactive Map Coming Soon

Accessibility

Our museum is committed to being accessible to all visitors:

  • Wheelchair accessible entrances and elevators
  • Accessible restrooms on all floors
  • Wheelchairs available for loan (free of charge)
  • Service animals welcome
  • Audio guides and large-print materials available
  • Assistive listening devices for guided tours

For specific accessibility questions or to request accommodations, please contact us at accessibility@museum.com or call (123) 456-7890.

Dining

Museum Café

Our café offers a selection of fresh salads, sandwiches, pastries, and beverages.

Hours: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM (Tuesday - Sunday)

Rooftop Restaurant

Enjoy fine dining with panoramic city views at our rooftop restaurant.

Hours: 11:30 AM - 9:00 PM (Tuesday - Sunday)

Reservations recommended: (123) 456-7891

Museum Shop

The Museum Shop offers a wide range of items including:

  • Books and exhibition catalogs
  • Art prints and posters
  • Jewelry and accessories
  • Home decor and gifts
  • Educational toys for children

Hours: 10:00 AM - 5:30 PM (Tuesday - Sunday)

Museum members receive a 10% discount on all purchases.

Online shopping available at shop.museum.com

Ready to Visit?

Check out our current exhibitions and book your tickets today!
